{"tid":2118386,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國：90萬公務員、醫護加薪至少2%  政府答謝疫情間付出","createTime":"2020-07-21T12:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:40:01.000Z","uid":227801,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb003a9db3dc44f2508188d06baca110b621f8c","tid":2118386,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2701572/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B90%E8%90%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%912-%20%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AD%94%E8%AC%9D%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%96%93%E4%BB%98%E5%87%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2701572%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B90%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%25912-%2520%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AD%2594%25E8%25AC%259D%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%2587%25BA&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjyT1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=ba300e4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2701572/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B90%E8%90%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%912-%20%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AD%94%E8%AC%9D%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%96%93%E4%BB%98%E5%87%BA</a><br />\n英國疫情持續之際，英國政府為答謝公共部門人員在新冠肺炎疫情上的付出，宣布對近90萬人加薪，加薪幅度更超過通脹水平。英國財相辛偉誠（Rishi Sunak）形容，在最近數個月，更能看到公共部門人員的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n加薪計劃會在2020年至2021年財政年度實行。英格蘭的教師、全英國的牙醫及醫生的加薪幅度較大，分別為3.1%及2.8%。<br />\n<br />\n而在英格蘭及威爾斯的警察、監獄人員及國家刑事局 （National Crime Agency）的人員將會提高2.5%，而英國各地的武裝部隊將獲加薪2%，司法及高級公務員亦同獲加薪2%。<br />\n<br />\n辛偉誠指：<br />\n<br />\n「在過去的幾個月中，更能突顯我們以往所知道，公共部門人員為我國家作出重要貢獻，並且在我們需要他們時，可以依靠他們。」<br />\n<br />\n（These past months have underlined what we always knew, that our public sector workers make a vital contribution to our country and that we can rely on them when we need them.）"},{"pid":"5f16e96cd674b84f2098b5d592a2c0eb502cfd50","tid":2118386,"uid":338439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"當地人工1700磅一個月（護士）"},{"pid":"0dcdfd448b757d3ecb3b50fd0638f43c4c0425c7","tid":2118386,"uid":29080,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"香港：凍薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92c1ed81a92c885670293787b6543c5167637b3","tid":2118386,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:17:56.000Z","msg":"香港：黑警無限津貼代加人工"},{"pid":"53d4bd658b77aec4f37038abf59fd95e4b637735","tid":2118386,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/borisjohnson/status/1285483788684992512?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fborisjohnson%2Fstatus%2F1285483788684992512%3Fs%3D21&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjyT1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=33511eb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fborisjohnson%2Fstatus%2F1285483788684992512%3Fs%3D21&h=7afbd348\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/borisjohnson/status/1285483788684992512?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"1389f6f9aa6ac2ddb79347d5692bdb58ca313d22","tid":2118386,"uid":51920,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"教畜點解排先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903e1d7dcc42481a62e65be429685b526e80be36","tid":2118386,"uid":294121,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"香港個堆淨係識偷懶平時又無野DO<br />\nWFH期間捐返D人工出黎俾市民就差唔多"},{"pid":"d4d6f370859741d17c9b04e533768995c443f2c2","tid":2118386,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:24:27.000Z","msg":"啲留言屌老師無做野都有得加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face